But the man just waved off.
"One says this, the other says that," he makes a dark face.
The Ostrava region thus becomes a large "deregulatory laboratory".
After the New Year, this deregulation is imminent for most rental apartments in the Czech Republic, whose tenants have not yet paid a market-oriented rent.
Aktuálně.cz therefore decided to visit this "laboratory" in person.
